      <title>中国粮食需求减弱给世界农民带来麻烦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/china-s-fading-hunger-for-grain-spells-trouble-for-world-farmers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着经济危机不断加深，中国各地的仓库里都堆满了粮食，全球农民不得不应对其最大客户之一的经济长期放缓的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/china-s-fading-hunger-for-grain-spells-trouble-for-world-farmers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 01:45:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济数据令人失望，中国股市在香港下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/chinese-stocks-drop-in-hong-kong-after-economic-data-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宏观数据普遍走弱，打击了人们对在缺乏全面刺激措施的情况下经济出现大幅反弹的乐观情绪，导致香港上市的中国股票指数下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/chinese-stocks-drop-in-hong-kong-after-economic-data-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 01:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
